tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Sam-Fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a>宣布了他即将发行的第三张专辑《People Watching》的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-live-in-newcastle-setlist-photos-3454626">萨姆·芬德在纽卡斯尔现场演出：明星云集的卡通庆祝活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>《People Watching》由 Fender 与他的乐队成员 Dean Thompson、Joe Atkinson、制作人 Markus Dravs 以及<a href="/artists/The-War-on-Drugs">The War on Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 共同制作，预计于 2025 年 2 月 21 日通过 Polydor 发行。您可以<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订黑胶唱片。</p><p>一份新闻稿将芬德的专辑描述为“他向前迈出的下一步”，承诺提供“丰富多彩的故事和对日常人物日常生活但往往非凡的生活的观察”。</p><p>专辑封面照片由已故的著名社会纪实摄影师 Tish Murtha 拍摄，他在南希尔兹长大，记录了泰恩河畔纽卡斯尔的边缘化社区和工薪阶层的生活。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812392" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812392" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="萨姆·芬德《People Watching》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812392" class="wp-caption-text">萨姆·芬德《People Watching》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“人们在观看”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“人们在观看”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“怀旧的谎言”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“抬起头”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“疯狂的长谎言”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“保持距离”</strong><br /> <strong>6.《崩溃的帝国》</strong><br /> <strong>7.“再近一点”</strong><br /> <strong>8.《控制我》</strong><br /> <strong>9.《电视晚餐》</strong><br /> <strong>10.“沉重的东西”</strong><br /> <strong>11.《记住我的名字》</strong></p><p>专辑的第一批品尝者将以主打单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-new-single-people-watching-and-teases-album-news-3810920">People Watching</a> ”的形式抵达，该单曲定于本周五（11 月 15 日）发行。这位北希尔兹歌手兼作曲家上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-shares-preview-of-new-single-people-watching-3809969">分享了这首歌的片段</a>。</p><p> Fender 在 Instagram 上发帖感谢粉丝们的“耐心等待”，并分享了这幅单幅作品的特色是 Murtha 拍摄的“南希尔兹路上”的照片。</p><p> “能够用她的艺术来帮助讲述专辑的故事是一种荣幸，”他说。您可以在<a href="https://shop.samfender.com/products/people-watching-cd-single" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>预订包含 B 面“Me And The Dog”的单曲 CD，并<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/PWListen" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预先保存曲目。</p><p> Fender 在他的 Instagram 帐户上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-people-watching-single-surrogate-mother-to-me-3811192">透露了即将发行的单曲背后的故事</a>，并分享说这首歌是关于一个“对我来说就像代孕母亲一样，于去年 11 月去世的人”的故事。最后我在她身边，睡在她旁边的椅子上。这是关于我脑子里所想的事情，往返于那个地方和家。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这有点讽刺，因为她给了我登上舞台的信心，而且她总是说‘为什么你在获奖感言中没有提到我的名字’。但现在整首歌（和专辑）都与她联系在一起。我希望无论她现在身在何处，她都会低下头说‘是时候了，孩子’。” </p><figure id="attachment_3812390" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812390" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812390" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1.jpg" alt="萨姆·芬德。图片来源：麦克·斯科特" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-Credit-Mac-Scott-1-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812390" class="wp-caption-text">萨姆·芬德。图片来源：麦克·斯科特</figcaption></figure><p>8 月 3 日，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-plays-live-debut-for-two-unreleased-songs-people-watching-and-nostalgia-lies-3780786">首次现场演唱了《People Watching》，以及另一首未发行的歌曲《Nostalgia&#39;s Lie》</a> ，这两首歌曲都将出现在他期待已久的第三张专辑中。</p><p>上个月，Fender 开玩笑说这张专辑已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-album-is-finished-and-mastered-3799886">完成并“掌握”了</a>，他在 Instagram 上分享了工作室的一系列照片和视频，并透露他在制作这张专辑时得到了 Granduciel 的意见。</p><p> Fender 在他的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">《Hypersonic Missiles》</a>和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">Seventeen Going Under</a> 》之间留出了两年的时间间隔，而《Seventeen Going Under》和他的第三张专辑之间也有近四年的时间间隔。</p><p>但他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-provides-new-album-update-and-admits-he-rushed-to-get-seventeen-going-under-out-3752305">今年早些时候承认，他“匆忙”完成了他的上一张专辑</a>。在接受天空艺术频道<i>约翰逊和诺夫勒音乐传奇</i>节目采访时，芬德分享道：“第三个我们开始匆忙，我想，‘不，我们必须花时间’。”</p><p> “我想尽我所能。我宁愿迟到而精彩，也不愿早到而糟糕。到目前为止我们所取得的成果让我欣喜若狂，但我想给予它更多的时间和更多的思考。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DB9T7vctGv4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.